        "id": "lcd-st7789",
        "name": {
          "en": "SPI LCD（ATK-MD0240）",
          "zh-CN": "SPI 屏 (ATK-MD0240)"
        },
        "interface": "SPI",
        "mounting": "accessory",
        "pinLocked": false,
        "port": 0,
        "model": "ST7789",
        "width": 320,
        "height": 240,
        "pixelFormat": "RGB565",
        "backlight": "CUSTOM",
        "blPwmChannel": 0,
        "timing": {
          "syncMode": "VH",
          "clkEdge": "rising"
        },
        "pins": {
          "SPI": [
            {
              "role": "rst",
              "expanderId": "io-expander-xl9555",
              "expanderPin": 10
            },
            {
              "role": "power",
              "expanderId": "io-expander-xl9555",
              "expanderPin": 11
            },
            {
              "role": "bl",
              "expanderId": "io-expander-xl9555",
              "expanderPin": 8
            },
            {
              "role": "sck",
              "gpio": 12
            },
            {
              "role": "mosi",
              "gpio": 11
            },
            {
              "role": "cs",
              "gpio": 21
            },
            {
              "role": "dc",
              "gpio": 40
            }
          ]
        },
        "kconfig": null,
        "note": {
          "en": "SPI LCD header (U2). Data on fixed MCU GPIOs (sck=IO12, mosi=IO11, cs=IO21, dc=IO40); backlight/reset/power are driven via the XL9555 expander (bl=#8, rst=SLCD_RST #10, power=SLCD_PWR #11). The ESP SPI-LCD driver is configured rst_io=-1 because reset is toggled through the expander, not a direct GPIO. ST7789 is the shipped/default panel; the header accepts any compatible SPI panel on these pins.",
          "zh-CN": "SPI LCD 排针（U2）。数据走固定 MCU GPIO（sck=IO12, mosi=IO11, cs=IO21, dc=IO40）；背光/复位/电源经 XL9555 扩展器驱动（bl=#8, rst=SLCD_RST #10, power=SLCD_PWR #11）。ESP SPI-LCD 驱动配置 rst_io=-1，因为复位是经扩展器拉的、非直连 GPIO。ST7789 是随板/默认屏，该排针可换插任意兼容 SPI 屏，用这组脚。"
        }
      },
