          "en": "Micro SD card on the SPI1 header (enable via ENABLE_DNESP32S3_SDCARD). SPI mode: sck=IO12, mosi=IO11, miso=IO13, cs=IO2 (TUYA_SPI1). __board_register_sd() only configures pinmux; the SD/file-system stack is driven by the SDK SPI + FS components. No card-detect pin is wired.",
          "zh-CN": "Micro SD 卡，接 SPI1 排针（通过 ENABLE_DNESP32S3_SDCARD 使能）。SPI 模式：sck=IO12、mosi=IO11、miso=IO13、cs=IO2（TUYA_SPI1）。__board_register_sd() 仅配置 pinmux；SD/文件系统栈由 SDK 的 SPI + FS 组件驱动。未接卡检测引脚。"
